{"tid":691182,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"聽廣東歌嘅入嚟投票 - 你哋用開咩串流app？","createTime":"2018-06-05T13:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T03:22:21.000Z","uid":184592,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"0a2e816e95b773b006a9989f4e27fd7142542e64","tid":691182,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T13:08:24.000Z","msg":"係咁嘅，香港人已經唔睇《勁歌金曲》、少聽咗收音機，旺角CD街舖又已滅絶，香港人普遍已經唔知有乜新歌<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，所以小弟執咗一系列 YouTube playlist，方便大家上住連登都可以聽歌。礙於新歌太多，而小弟私人時間有限，只可以根據每週903排行榜update playlist<br />\n<br />\n詳情可以睇呢個post嘅整合：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/671991/page/4\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/671991/page/4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">&gt;&gt;依家我想<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">推展呢個計劃至串流app</span></strong>，但問題係香港串流用戶好似好分散，咁不如搞個投票，你用開邊個app 就俾正評，正評最多我就用嗰個app <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>投票2018年6月19日22:00結束</strong>&lt;&lt;</div></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n※ 如果唔可以用免費用戶身份製作playlist，咁我就唔會用嗰個app"},{"pid":"d183ac888548feba3659ed9e06c603d68c48bf91","tid":691182,"uid":184592,"like":83,"dislike":18,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T13:09:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">用<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">Apple Music</span></strong>請正評此回覆</span>"},{"pid":"1861372c1e48fdaa7bbc340c00960e171855e796","tid":691182,"uid":26156,"like":4,"dislike":57,"score":-53,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T13:10:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45650b469f625ef3332dbebac78a9ef7c23bb9b4","tid":691182,"uid":184592,"like":87,"dislike":42,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T13:10:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">用<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">JOOX</span></strong>請正評此回覆</span>"},{"pid":"1ab1094f040113201b2da9e84225f8b95b28e3e1","tid":691182,"uid":184592,"like":126,"dislike":14,"score":112,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T13:11:01.0